  "body": "<p>Hi, it's <a href=\"http://watersfive.typepad.com/\">Jamie</a> here! One of the perks to working on the Amy Tangerine team is going to different events. In October, Amy taught workshops at the first ever <a href=\"http://www.sanrio.com/hellokittycon/\">Hello Kitty Con</a>. She had me go around and take some photos of the show floor. It was super fun! The amount of Hello Kitty lovers was amazing to be around. There were so many fans, the happiness was rather contagious.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309636937-GYWRMTTZR04R70YET3RC/4a-IMG_1795.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4b-IMG_1796.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309704971-N1EA7TY0PC4UTSMFU7S3/4b-IMG_1796.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"4c-IMG_1799.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309705577-2GPEO2Y1MELGYVORW93Z/4c-IMG_1799.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4d-IMG_1805.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309706337-8BM4LIL79WNVBULUZAAE/4d-IMG_1805.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The marketplace to buy everything Hello Kitty was decorated so cute! I felt like I was in a little Japanese village.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309747419-HTN4XEDHY3VMVQ6HI3MP/4e-IMG_1802.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>LA Ink was there doing free Hello Kitty tattoos!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309758667-3RIVSRF64TBS51T7H1WK/4f-IMG_1812.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Cutest light color changing station! And Sephora dolling people up with their adorable Hello Kitty line.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309782376-48WTDT29WDKYDIJ2QHDL/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Probably the neatest exhibit, the collection of Sanrio bags through the years! I recognize quite a few of those bags, I may have even hoarded them for future gift wrapping options!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309797870-4I7U78BSHU2W3LLH815Z/4h-IMG_1815.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Cutest disposable cardboard Sanrio chairs, yes!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309816140-4HPWETNJJE40G4VH0VDD/4i-IMG_1809.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The vintage village displayed many of the Hello Kitty toys through the years. Memories!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309833772-31DLF0BPB49BTPDK8910/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>What a memorable day, I am so thrilled that Sanrio celebrated Hello Kitty's 40th!</p><p>Also wanted to include that I had the honor of working with <a href=\"http://papercamellia.com/collections/current-month-s-kits/products/december-2014-main-scrapbook-kit\">Paper Camellia's December Kit</a>. It featured a ton of <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=stitched&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fsearch%2Easpx%3FKeywords%3Damy%2Btangerine%2Bstitched%2B2014\">Amy's Stitched line </a>which was so fun to work with! Here are the layouts I made with the kit. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309859836-WACDU98SMQHIS4U83Z4V/4k-polarelsie.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309880620-I76R8UL28JO9QDFWCN2D/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Here's the <a href=\"http://papercamellia.com/collections/current-month-s-kits/products/december-2014-main-scrapbook-kit\">main kit</a> I worked with.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309901561-OU0DJ9NI9XWZ44ZXC8C3/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Paper Camellia is also going to be giving away some goodies on their <a href=\"http://papercamellia.com/blogs/papercamelliablog/16100088-our-december-guest\">blog</a>! Head over there to check it out, good luck!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}